入rc 搵人幫捉既<br />\n未有家族頻 唯有rc 講住野先"},{"pid":"8a677f6cf1fce4d95535e0caebb0159751550cf3","tid":508160,"uid":117962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"宜家無得玩?"},{"pid":"7d49e9c1318f91d3830c751abfcffa17f5cff8a8","tid":508160,"uid":38983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T06:25:39.000Z","msg":"職又唔洗就 技能屋搞掂哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲自動打怪 咁就冇左同人升lv吹水啦<br />\n個個掛係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你話唔係打手 純粹想多人玩<br />\n咁玩水藍魔力啦<br />\n又多人又好玩 起碼冇以上既膠功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}